Package: comma
Title: Comparative Methylomics for Microbial Analysis
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Carl", "Stone", , "carl.j.stone@vanderbilt.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0232-5223"))
Description: Analyze bacterial DNA methylation from Oxford Nanopore sequencing
    data. Supports genome-wide characterization of methylation patterns across
    multiple modification types (6mA, 5mC, 4mC), annotation of methylation
    sites relative to genomic features, and identification of differentially
    methylated sites between conditions. Accepts input from modkit pileup
    (primary), Dorado BAM, and Megalodon (legacy) callers.
